title: Episode 152: It Hurts so Much it's Beautiful (Feat. Venus Cuffs)
itunes:title: Episode 152: It Hurts so Much it's Beautiful (Feat. Venus Cuffs)
description:
On this week's special episode of Lip Service, Venus Cuffs, a dominatrix joins the ladies and things get wild! Venus describes how she entered the community, what she has done to her 'clients,' how much these people are willing to pay, and much more! Angela and the girls even recruit a volunteer to allow Venus to demonstrate.
